dismissalText.commentary: Ian Bell c Hussey b Johnson 15 (29b 2x4 0x6 54m) SR: 51.72

dismissalComment.html: Gottim! And you have to say that was coming! Johnson's been turning the screw superbly since he came on, and this time Bell couldn't hold himself back - down the track, and a loose drive straight to mid-off, comfortably lodged in Mike Hussey's midriff

dismissalText.commentary: Kevin Pietersen c Symonds b Clark 82 (91b 4x4 3x6 143m) SR: 90.1

dismissalComment.html: another vast swipe ... and it's swirling, swirling, swirling down to Andrew Symonds, just inside the long-on boundary! A massive breakthrough for Australia, and Pietersen is gone, just when he was looking at his most dangerous

headshotImage.caption: MG Johnson headshot
headshotImage.longCaption: MG Johnson headshot

dismissalText.commentary: Paul Nixon lbw b Johnson 0 (4b 0x4 0x6 5m) SR: 0

dismissalComment.html: gone! Full, straight and that would've plucked out his leg stump. Excellent length from Johnson and with a touch of away swing to the left hander who, trying to work it to leg, was beaten by pace...and up goes the finger

dismissalText.commentary: Jamie Dalrymple c Gilchrist b McGrath 2 (8b 0x4 0x6 8m) SR: 25

dismissalComment.html: down the leg side, Dalymple tries to hook this and misses. Gilchrist politely asks the umpire who, after a couple of seconds, raises his finger! What a shocker that is. Replays indicate the ball hit his helmet, and Dalrymple trudges off fairly fuming

dismissalText.commentary: Jon Lewis c Ponting b Bracken 9 (9b 0x4 0x6 13m) SR: 100

dismissalComment.html: what a catch! A full toss which Lewis sliced off a thick outside edge just to Ponting's right at backward point, and he dived brilliantly taking the ball horizontally, one-handed. Quite superb fielding
